messages: RT @Pachangafiend: @KillBill345 I know a Sudanese who don't consider North Sudanese people real Africans. <--That person is right.
If my birth mother was alive she would have ZERO interest in my career. Her thing: "Can U cook well? Got man?" @KillBill345 @Pachangafiend
I totally idolize Whoopi Goldberg...so telling me that I resemble her is not a put-down. I hold her in very high esteem.
